{{vgname|文明帝國：超越地球|en=Civilization: Beyond Earth|cn=文明：太空|tw=文明帝國：超越地球}}是一款由[[Firaxis_Games|Firaxis Games]]开发的[[回合策略游戏|回合策略游戏]]，由[[2K_Games|2K Games]]發行，是[[文明系列|文明系列]]的第6部作品（但並非文明6，屬於外傳系列）。游戏对应[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[Mac_OS_X|Mac OS X]]及[[Linux|Linux]]平台，Windows PC版於2014年10月24日發行<ref name="Civilization.com">{{cite web|url = http://www.civilization.com/en/games/civilization-beyond-earth/|title = Sid Meier's Civilization: Beyond Earth|accessdate = 2014-11-18|archive-date = 2016-05-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160506095437/https://www.civilization.com/en/games/civilization-beyond-earth/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。而OS X及Linux版則於2014年11月26日及12月18日分別發行。

《文明帝國：超越地球》是《{{link-en|半人马座阿尔法星|Sid Meier's Alpha Centauri}}》的精神續作<ref name="Orland,K.">{{Cite web |url = http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2014/04/firaxis-takes-civilization-to-the-star-with-beyond-earth-announcement/ |title = Firaxis takes Civilization to the stars with Beyond Earth announcement |author = Kyle Orland |date = 2014-04-13 |publisher = Ars Technica |accessdate = 2016-06-06 |archive-date = 2014-10-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141026021543/http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2014/04/firaxis-takes-civilization-to-the-star-with-beyond-earth-announcement/ |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-04-12-firaxis-announces-sid-meiers-civilization-beyond-earth |title = Firaxis announces Sid Meier's Civilization: Beyond Earth |author = Wesley Yin-Poole |date = 2014-04-14 |publisher = Eurogamer |accessdate = 2016-06-06 |archive-date = 2019-11-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191106021918/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-04-12-firaxis-announces-sid-meiers-civilization-beyond-earth |dead-url = no }}</ref>。對比其他文明系列的遊戲，本作的設定頗為獨特。其背景設定於未來，隨著地球因為一次被稱為「巨大錯誤」的未描述的災難而變得不適居住，人類需要進行太空旅行並在外行星創建殖民地<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.polygon.com/2014/4/12/5600008/civilization-beyond-earth-trailer-screenshots-announcement-sid-meier |title = Sid Meier's Civilization: Beyond Earth will take humanity to space this fall |author = Dave Tach |date = 2014-04-12 |publisher = Polygon |accessdate = 2016-06-06 |archive-date = 2021-02-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210202160552/https://www.polygon.com/2014/4/12/5600008/civilization-beyond-earth-trailer-screenshots-announcement-sid-meier |dead-url = no }}</ref>。玩家將前往宇宙探索，初始為一個外星球，豐饒，天空城，真菌為三種世界類型，城市可以建立到外星和前哨站。<ref>{{cite web |url = http://games.sina.com.cn/j/n/2014-09-22/1116817732_5.shtml |title = 大作瘋狂來襲 10月單機遊戲發售預覽 |accessdate = 2014-11-18 |archive-date = 2016-08-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160804093355/http://games.sina.com.cn/j/n/2014-09-22/1116817732_5.shtml |dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 遊戲概況 ==
《文明帝國：超越地球》的構想及其玩法都是源自前作《文明帝國V》，而且地圖仍然使用著六角形地圖<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.escapistmagazine.com/articles/view/video-games/previews/11268- |title = Civilization: Beyond Earth Could Be Alpha Centauri 2 Without the Name |author = Greg Tito |date = 2014-04-13 |publisher = The Escapist |accessdate = 2016-06-05 |archive-date = 2019-09-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190926122604/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/articles/view/video-games/previews/11268- |dead-url = no }}</ref>。聯合首席設計師大衛·麥克唐納（David McDonough）表示《文明帝國：超越地球》及其前作《文明帝國V》的關係非常親密，兩者給予玩家的遊玩體驗非常類似，例如是城市、城市的基礎發展、不同的領導者、時間的推移、回合制度、建築改造及技術等的理念<ref name="Senior,T.">{{Cite web |url = http://www.pcgamer.com/civilization-beyond-earth-interview-everything-you-need-to-know-about-the-new-factions-aliens-technology-and-more/#page-3 |title = Civilization: Beyond Earth interview - everything you need to know about the new factions, aliens, technology and more |author = Tom Senior |date = 2014-04-12 |publisher = PC Gamer UK |accessdate = 2016-06-05 |archive-date = 2021-01-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210121184815/https://www.pcgamer.com/civilization-beyond-earth-interview-everything-you-need-to-know-about-the-new-factions-aliens-technology-and-more/#page-3 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

有別於以往作品，本作在不同的部分都作出了重大的改變。在以往的作品，玩家需要選擇一位歷史人物作為其文明的領導者，而這些歷史人物均基於歷史數據而前設了其個人性格。但於本作中，玩家能於遊戲開始前選擇以哪一支贊助商成為自己的探險隊、用什麼類型的太空船前往外星球、及帶誰人及什麼物資前往新世界，這使玩家能客制化自己的文明<ref name="gamer_1">{{cite web |url = http://gnn.gamer.com.tw/3/95713.html |title = 創造人類未來！《文明帝國》系列發表最新作《文明帝國：超越地球》 |accessdate = 2014-11-18 |archive-date = 2016-08-28 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160828140826/http://gnn.gamer.com.tw/3/95713.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。此外，早期的決策對遊戲有一個顯著的影響。在以往作品中出現的線性科技樹，將於本作中被變更為「高科技網絡」，並強制玩家只能在每次選擇其中一個方向。而且遊戲是不允許文明之間作出科技交易（雖然技術仍可被他人盜去），因此令玩家幾乎不可能在遊戲中解鎖所有科技<ref name="gamer_1" />。

傾向性是人類進步史上的一個極為重要及用途廣泛的哲學思想，因其能夠使玩家的科技得以進步及解鎖獨特的單位。傾向性有三種，分別是和諧、至高和純正，而且玩家能以不同的傾向性組合方式結束遊戲<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.civilopedia.info/civilopediabe/zh-hant-hk/CONCEPT_AFFINITY.aspx |title = 遊戲概念－傾向性 |publisher = Firaxis |accessdate = 2016-06-06 |archive-date = 2017-01-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170112000926/http://www.civilopedia.info/civilopediabe/zh-hant-hk/CONCEPT_AFFINITY.aspx |dead-url = no }}</ref>。和諧傾向性旨在理解和融合星球的外星生態，能通過基因改造使殖民者更為適應外星生態環境，及能馴服野生的外星動物；至高傾向性傾向相信先進科技，會利用高效率的單位互相扶助；純正傾向性則像孤立主義，以興建威力強大的防禦設施及試圖將行星地球化為主要目的。每種傾向性都可開啟某些潛在的勝利條件，一旦完全解鎖便能獲得勝利<ref name="Senior,T."/><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/04/12/firaxis-revisits-alpha-centauri-territory-with-civilization-beyond-earth |title = Firaxis Revisits Alpha Centauri with Civilization: Beyond Earth |author = Dan Stapleton |date = 2014-04-12 |publisher = IGN |accessdate = 2016-06-06 |archive-date = 2020-12-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201203175550/https://www.ign.com/articles/2014/04/12/firaxis-revisits-alpha-centauri-territory-with-civilization-beyond-earth |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 開發 ==
《文明帝國：超越地球》在2014年4月12日由[[Firaxis_Games|Firaxis Games]]於[[波士頓|波士頓]]舉辦的PAX活動中公佈<ref name="Orland,K."/>。

LORE是一款被用於前作《文明帝國V》及本作的圖形引擎。有別於[[OpenGL|OpenGL]]及直至版本11前的[[Direct3D|Direct3D]]，LORE引擎採用了在[[Mantle_(API)|Mantle]]、Direct3D 12及[[Vulkan_(API)|Vulkan]]上實施的低CPU管理負擔。雖然Firaxis正式表示遊戲支援Mantle，但卻沒有公佈遊戲同樣支援Direct3D 12或Vulkan。

在設計「高科技網絡」時，遊戲開發團隊先從維基百科閱讀有關另一款遊戲「{{Tsl|en|Sid Meier's Alpha Centauri|席德·梅爾的半人馬座阿爾法星|半人馬座阿爾法星}}」的文章，及閱讀在文章中被列作布賴恩·雷諾茲（Brian Reynolds）（半人马座阿尔法星的設計師）視為靈感來源的書籍<ref name="Senior,T."/>。遊戲內所發生的事件的時間被設成距離現今大約200至300年，而且開發團隊亦使用現代空間科學，例如參考[[太空探索科技公司|SpaceX]]的發射及紀錄片《[[宇宙時空之旅|宇宙時空之旅]]》的不同集數，以培養他們對遊戲的未來的願景<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.destructoid.com/civilization-beyond-earth-designers-inspired-by-cosmos-273439.phtml |title = Civilization: Beyond Earth designers inspired by Cosmos |author = Darren Nakamura |date = 2014-04-18 |publisher = Destructoid |accessdate = 2016-06-06 |archive-date = 2017-01-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170112040107/https://www.destructoid.com/civilization-beyond-earth-designers-inspired-by-cosmos-273439.phtml |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2014年8月，Firaxis Games及其母公司[[Take-Two_Interactive|Take-Two Interactive]]在沒有警告的情況下，將澳洲零售版和數位版的價錢從$49.95美元調整至$89.95美元，使這兩間公司在同月於遊戲社區中飽受非議<ref name="Serrels,M.">{{Cite web |url = http://www.kotaku.com.au/2014/08/if-youre-going-to-rip-off-australian-gamers-at-least-hide-your-tracks/ |title = If You're Going To Rip Off Australian Gamers, At Least Hide Your Tracks. |author = Mark Serrels |date = 2014-08-25 |publisher = Kotaku |accessdate = 2016-06-06 |archive-date = 2021-03-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210307084251/https://www.kotaku.com.au/2014/08/if-youre-going-to-rip-off-australian-gamers-at-least-hide-your-tracks/ |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Colwill,T.">{{Cite web |url = http://games.on.net/2014/08/civilization-beyond-earth-just-went-up-40-on-steam/ |title = Civilization: Beyond Earth just went up $40 on |author = Tim Colwill |date = 2014-08-24 |publisher = Games.on.net |accessdate = 2016-06-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151121202855/http://games.on.net/2014/08/civilization-beyond-earth-just-went-up-40-on-steam/ |archive-date = 2015-11-21 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>。其後有眾多遊戲刊物及消費者批評兩間公司的這種舉動，並指價錢調整與澳洲的稅項有關<ref name="Serrels,M."/><ref name="Colwill,T."/>。

2015年初，Firaxis宣布開發新作《{{tsl|en|Sid Meier's Starships|席德·梅爾的星際戰艦}}（Sid Meier's Starships）》，並將背景設定為《文明帝國：超越地球》的數百年後，讓玩家指揮星際艦隊在不同星系航行並爭奪它們的支持<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://gnn.gamer.com.tw/5/112125.html |title = 【試玩】體驗《席德梅爾：星際戰艦》回合制戰略 指揮星際艦隊航行浩瀚宇宙間爭奪勢力 |date = 2015-03-16 |publisher = 巴哈姆特電玩資訊站 |accessdate = 2016-06-06 |archive-date = 2017-01-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170112080647/https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/5/112125.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。此遊戲於2015年3月發行，並能交叉連接至《文明帝國：超越地球》<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.gamespot.com/articles/firaxis-reveals-new-interstellar-strategy-game-sid/1100-6424728/ |title = Firaxis Reveals New Interstellar Strategy Game, Sid Meier's Starships |author = Eddie Makuch |date = 2015-01-20 |publisher = Gamespot |accessdate = 2016-06-06 |archive-date = 2021-02-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210208082151/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/firaxis-reveals-new-interstellar-strategy-game-sid/1100-6424728/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 潮起 ==
[[File:Civilization_Beyond_Earth_Rising_Tide_Cover.jpg|缩略图]]
《潮起》為本作的首張資料片，於2015年3月28日由Firaxis Games宣佈，並於同年10月9日發行<ref name="Tack,D.">{{Cite web |url = http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2015/05/18/civilization-beyond-earth-rising-tide-emerges-from-the-deep.aspx? |title = Civilization: Beyond Earth – Rising Tide Emerges From The Deep |author = Daniel Tack |date = 2015-05-18 |publisher = Game Informer |accessdate = 2016-06-06 |archive-date = 2021-01-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210126061413/https://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2015/05/18/civilization-beyond-earth-rising-tide-emerges-from-the-deep.aspx |dead-url = no }}</ref>。顧名思義，《潮起》帶來了全新的海洋遊戲機制，同時亦大幅度改善了原有的系統。《潮起》令玩家能於海洋格上建造城市及不同的改良設施，而且海上城市能移動至鄰近一格的位置<ref name="Tack,D." /><ref name="gamer_2">{{Cite web |url = http://gnn.gamer.com.tw/6/122496.html |title = 【試玩】體驗《文明帝國：超越地球 - 潮起》新機制 打造一片屬於自己的海洋世界 |date = 2015-10-12 |publisher = 巴哈姆特電玩資訊站 |accessdate = 2016-06-06 |archive-date = 2017-01-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170112080813/https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/6/122496.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。此外，外交系統亦有重要變化。《潮起》的監製安德魯·弗雷德里克森（Andrew Frederiksen）表示在資料片中外交系統並非只新增了數個新按鈕或選項，而簡直是在代碼級別上重寫了遊戲的外交系統<ref name="Tack,D." />。在《潮起》中，每個文明都能選擇最多四個的人格特質，而除了第一個「特質」是依照所選文明決定外，其餘三個「政治」、「國內」、「軍事」特質則可以透過本次資料片新增的資源「外交資本」來購買並升級<ref name="gamer_2" />。

